snippet.title: Mera First Look REACTION - Justice League 2017 Amber Heard
snippet.description:
Justice League 2017 Mera today! Beyond The Trailer's reaction & review of our first look at Amber Heard in costume as Mera!
http://bit.ly/subscribeBTT

Justice League 2017 Mera today! Beyond The Trailer host Grace Randolph's reaction and review of our first look at Amber Heard in costume as Mera from Zack Snyder! A good match with Jason Momoa as Aquaman?  Share your own reaction to our first look at Amber Heard in costume as Mera before you see her in the full movie, Justice League, in 2017!
